{"tid":1891063,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"政府批左三百億俾支那狗，本地手足一蚊都無。","createTime":"2020-02-21T14:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T03:49:49.000Z","uid":126621,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d14c2d4b7d9c32dcd710eeff739422033cd7bf81","tid":1891063,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:18:40.000Z","msg":"立法會財務委員會以59票贊成，3票反對，通過政府300億元防疫抗疫基金撥款申請。<br />\n<br />\n但由民主派議員提出的多項臨時動議，包括政府應向全港所有年滿18歲居民發放1萬元，渡過經濟難關，向開工不足人士派4000元津貼和失業津貼等，則<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全部被否決</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510048-20200221.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510048-20200221.htm&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=e5b7f70e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510048-20200221.htm&h=88064592\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510048-20200221.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好同我講300億我有份，我寧願唔撚醫都要你派錢</span></span>"},{"pid":"01766afe43cb8ad34a7664c340cb3509b690e8b9","tid":1891063,"uid":126621,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"300億/69人<br />\n每人有4.3億資源用"},{"pid":"e9c3b22af53493c92cea350e612fd614b8a62145","tid":1891063,"uid":74171,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"8.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fs1W1Kh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFs1W1Kh.jpg&h=ed0a65cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSend SMS 系統要1.5億？"},{"pid":"9eb1c2f270cb0f70be6e91273c9e60416dada863","tid":1891063,"uid":126621,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"買口罩 買防護衣呢d <br />\n唔應該係用基金錢買<br />\n而係醫護恒常支出黎<br />\n<br />\n到時 三百億咪又係拎黎買愛滋藥呀